Metro,Global,SMS,is,a,Nigerian,company,that,provides,SMS,and,voice,SMS,services,Users,are,only,charged,for,messages,that,are,successfully,delivered,Developers,can,integrate,with,the,Metro,Global,SMS,messaging,gateway,via,REST,API,This,allows,them,to,deliver,messages,and,check,their,balances,from,within,their,own,websites,or,applications